            {
                "uuid": "65e518c60839428a957454605ee5c2d7",
                "template": "C-FZ-UNIX-LNX-Chrony",
                "name": "C-FZ-UNIX-LNX-Chrony",
                "description": "## Overview\n\nThis template will parse the various types of data from the acquisition result of chronyc tracking command.  \nThis allows you to detect the change of the time of displacement and Stratum by chrony.",
                "groups": [
                    {
                        "name": "C-FZ-UNIX-LNX"
                    }
                ],
                "items": [
                    {
                        "uuid": "bd9feff70f4a4054962ac66445b8d0ec",
                        "name": "Get tracking",
                        "key": "chronyc.tracking",
                        "history": "90d",
                        "value_type": "TEXT",
                        "description": "This is the estimated local offset on the last clock update.",
                        "preprocessing": [
                            {
                                "type": "JAVASCRIPT",
                                "parameters": [
                                    "function toCamelCase(str) {\n  return str\n    .replace(/(?:^\\w|[A-Z]|\\b\\w|\\s+)/g, function(match, index) {\n      if (index === 0) {\n        return match.toLowerCase();\n      }\n      return match.toUpperCase();\n    })\n    .replace(/\\s+/g, ''); // \u0412\u0438\u0434\u0430\u043b\u044f\u0454\u043c\u043e \u0432\u0441\u0456 \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0431\u0456\u043b\u0438\n}\n\n// \u0420\u043e\u0437\u0431\u0438\u0442\u0438 \u0442\u0435\u043a\u0441\u0442 \u043d\u0430 \u0440\u044f\u0434\u043a\u0438\nvar lines = value.split(\"\\n\");\nvar result = {};\n\n// \u041e\u0431\u0440\u043e\u0431\u0438\u0442\u0438 \u043a\u043e\u0436\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u0440\u044f\u0434\u043e\u043a\nfor (var i = 0; i < lines.length; i++) {\n  var line = lines[i];\n  var idx = line.indexOf(\":\");\n  if (idx !== -1) {\n    var key = line.slice(0, idx).trim(); // \u0412\u0456\u0434\u0440\u0456\u0437\u0430\u0454\u043c\u043e \u0442\u0456\u043b\u044c\u043a\u0438 \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0431\u0456\u043b\u0438\n    var value = line.slice(idx + 1).trim();\n\n    // \u041f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0442\u0432\u043e\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0438 \u043a\u043b\u044e\u0447 \u043d\u0430 camelCase\n    key = toCamelCase(key);\n\n    result[key] = value;\n  }\n}\n\n// \u041f\u043e\u043a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0442\u0438 \u0440\u0435\u0437\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0430\u0442\nreturn JSON.stringify(result, null, 2);"
                                ]
                            }
                        ],
                        "tags": [
                            {
                                "tag": "Metric",
                                "value": "Raw"
                            },
                            {
                                "tag": "Type",
                                "value": "Source"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
